comments: Jokic (DEN) moves out of his screening position and makes a natural move toward the basket as marginal contact takes place with Ingles (UTA).
Murray (DEN) clears the lane within three seconds.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Harris' (DEN) path and does not deliver the contact.
Barton (DEN) avoids making contact with Mitchell (UTA) during his drive to the basket.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact with Mitchell's (UTA) side after his gather.

Jokic (DEN) firms up in his screening position in Crowder's (UTA) path and does not deliver the contact. As Jokic firms up on his left leg from a legal position, some incidental foot to foot contact occurs with Crowder.
Ingles (UTA) makes slight contact with Jokic's (DEN) arms at the end of his drive, but does not affect his ability to pass.
[Observable in enhanced video] Millsap (DEN) receives the pass and takes more than two steps after his gather.
Jokic (DEN) is in the lane for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
After initial contact during the screen, Jokic (DEN) slightly extends into Ingles' (UTA) path, but the contact is marginal and does not affect his ability to defend.
Ingles (UTA) briefly has his arm around Murray's (DEN) midsection before correcting.
[Observable in enhanced video] Harris (DEN) steps out of bounds along the sideline after receiving the pass.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in O'Neale's (UTA) path and does not deliver the contact.

The crew communicated with the Replay Center to determine if Gobert (UTA) committed a goaltending violation as he defended Jokic's (DEN) shot attempt. After review, it was determined that Gobert cleanly blocked the shot attempt before it reached its apex.

LAR shows O'Neale (UTA) places, but does not extend, his hand against Barton's (DEN) backside as they each attempt to gain control the ball. Barton's reaction is not consistent with the amount of contact.
Harris (DEN) initiates some body with O'Neale (UTA), but does not affect his ability to gain control of the ball.
Barton (DEN) grabs Mitchell (UTA) around the waist and initiates contact during the inbound that affects his SQBR and causes him to fall to the floor.
Murray (DEN) commits the take foul on Ingles (UTA).
Murray (DEN) commits the take foul on Ingles (UTA).
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Ingles' (UTA) path and does not deliver contact.
Gobert (UTA) extends his right hand against Murray's (DEN) midsection and affects his driving shot attempt. The contact occurs after Murray's gather.
Harris (DEN) commits the take foul on Ingles (UTA).
Barton (DEN) briefly places his hands on O'Neale (UTA) but disengages without affecting his ability to defend the inbound.
[Observable in enhanced video] Jokic (DEN) moves his pivot foot heel-to-toe.
Murray (DEN) commits the take foul on Gobert (UTA).
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Ingles' (UTA) defensive path and does not deliver the contact.
